    "DeepTraSynergy surpasses conventional and advanced models in predicting synergistic drug combinations on DrugCombDB and Oncology-Screen datasets, achieving accuracy values of 0.7715 and 0.8052, respectively.",
    "The evaluation of each component of DeepTraSynergy demonstrates its effectiveness, particularly highlighting the significance of incorporating protein-protein interaction networks in improving the prediction of synergistic drug combinations (Rafiei et al., 2023).",
    "In conclusion, the attention technique analyses historical data concurrently, enabling the application of correlation with distant tokens without reduction, in contrast to the RNN, where only one hidden state is available.",
    "Furthermore, BERT have been used in drug discovery endeavors and have greatly improved natural language presentation by employing DL (Devlin et al., 2018).",
    "For DTI applications, the transformer model may be easily included in the prevalent RNN-based QSAR modelling."
